Oh, and I forgot to mention in my comment on AO3, you're getting speech tags incorrectly.
If the dialogue has a dialogue tag attached, end it with a comma, then make the tag lowercase.
If it ends with a ? or !, then put it in place of the comma, but keep the tag lowercase. Unless of course it needs to be capitalized for other reasons, like being a proper noun.

>"Bird ladies sure are pretty," said Anon.
